  syslog-ng-3.4.8.ebuild, syslog-ng-3.5.4.1.ebuild:
  add support for reading Process Accounting files (EXPERIMENTAL, Linux only)
  (bug #498884)

  10 Jun 2014; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> syslog-ng-3.4.7.ebuild:
  Mark s390/sh stable.

